title: The.Cougar.S01E07
description:
Season 1, Episode 7:

From the creator of The Bachelor comes a game changing, provocative new reality show that redefines the rules of dating. One sexy, single, sophisticated woman is set up with younger men all vying for her attention. Through a series of weekly challenges, the men will have to prove that they have what it takes to satisfy a woman her age and avoid the kiss of death: a kiss on the cheek. Watch as she narrows her choices from 20 to 10 to 5, ultimately choosing one lucky man to be her soul mate.
